This plugin provides the ability to autoload plugins on demand, create 
global functions and commands and extend mksession with plugin support.

Features:
    â Autoloading plugins on FuncUndefined event.
    â Autoloading plugins when their command is called.
    â Autoloading plugins when their mapping is used.
    â Autoloading plugins when their functionality is required.
    â Displaying plugins' status.
    â Unloading and reloading plugins (useful for plugin developers).
    â Searching for a function number through registered plugins.
    â Checking function arguments before running a function.
    â Create a session file with plugin's data.

